<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span> صحيح - <span class="c2">((أحكام الجنائز)</span>) <span class="c2">(٦٠)</span>: ق.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>